{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c20072c409","title":"对二十二兵团清算贪污的时间界限的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"36533e9dd7","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"c20072c409"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e84f82ab3e","name":"王震","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"cd10194edb","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东的这个批语写在中共西北军区委员会1952年3月2日关于对二十二兵团贪污犯的处理意见给张邦英、张希钦并报中央军委、西北局的电报上。西北军区党委认为，清查处理二十二兵团的贪污犯，应从该部起义时查起，不宜一般地缩减这一时限。毛泽东不同意西北军区党委的这个意见。"},{"id":"82d8532ad0","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"d18796d342","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央新疆分局书记、中国人民解放军西北军区第二副司令员、新疆军区代司令员兼代政治委员王震，在1952年3月1日关于新疆党政军三反斗争情况给毛泽东并军委总政的报告中说，对二十二兵团清查贪污的时间界限，在三反运动开始时，他曾提出“把清算贪污的界限划定从改编建立共产党的领导（政治工作）以后算起”"}],"contents":[{"id":"c7eaa07622","type":"title","text":"对二十二兵团清算贫污的时间界限的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409"},{"id":"cd10194edb","type":"subtitle","text":"周吧：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409"},{"id":"82d8532ad0","type":"paragraph","text":"还是王震规定的时间（派去政治委员和建立共产党时开始算起），你与王震谈时请以此告他","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409"},{"id":"d18796d342","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c409"},{"id":"256ed3d1c3","type":"paragraph","text":"三月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c20072c40